Package languagemodel.calc

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ProbabilityCalculation
    Blueprint for a probability calculation, where a PathHandler with the task description is used to calculate the n-gram probability.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MapTreeNode<K extends java.util.List,V> Deprecated
    Class used to parallelize the calculation of n-gram probabilities in MaximumLikelihoodEstimation.
    MaximumLikelihoodEstimation
    A ProbabilityCalculation-function that computes n-gram probabilities based on n-gram and (n-1)-gram frequencies.
    nGramCalculator
    Class that retrieves a n-gram from a nGramDepot and calculates its probability.
    nGramSupplier
    Used in MaximumLikelihoodEstimation to calculate n-gram probabilities parallelized.
